{"tid":1025091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"塑造強人形象向民眾洗腦","createTime":"2019-02-17T05:47:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T08:13:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e946f457c1e550d362bdfba726b3becb56c5eac9","tid":1025091,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T05:47:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190217/20614325\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190217%2F20614325&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxrY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=2a251438\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190217%2F20614325&h=fe955f9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190217/20614325</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n塑造強人形象向民眾洗腦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190217/large/a0902a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190217%2Flarge%2Fa0902a.gif&h=7a7cb26b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n普京練習時摔倒奧運金牌選手穆德拉諾夫，但自己也弄傷手指。 美聯社<br />\n<br />\n赤膊騎馬、持槍打獵&hellip;&hellip;普京「勇猛」一面，不時出現在俄羅斯傳媒上，俄媒更說「猛男普京」月曆連年「熱賣」。普京喜歡展示硬漢形象，不只為了自我感覺良好，還希望民眾將他的「強悍」聯想到他抗衡西方、捍衞國家利益上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：與奧運柔道選手切磋普京遭女將摔倒克宮封殺失威照<br />\n<br />\n「馴服」猛虎北極熊<br />\n<br />\n自普京1999年開始掌權以來，俄羅斯官媒一直替他營造硬漢形象，除了柔道、騎馬打獵這些「基本功」外，還多次展現入水能游出水能飛的英姿，2009年他曾在全世界最深的湖潛下近1,400米，並且在水底向記者講話。他亦曾表演駕駛一級方程式跑車、戰機和超音速轟炸機。<br />\n<br />\n根據官方所講，普京不只受民眾「崇拜」，對動物也有一套，2008年他試過「馴服」東北虎，然後為牠量度牙齒，並且替牠安裝追蹤器。兩年後他再次出手，在俄羅斯北極地區「馴服」北極熊，在牠身上安裝訊號器。<br />\n<br />\n但一味勇猛也不成，克里姆林宮不忘間中展現普京鐵漢柔情及能文能武一面，除了多次溫柔擁抱大狗小狗，又試過摟着東北虎寶寶。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》資料室<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n與奧運柔道選手切磋 普京遭女將摔倒 克宮封殺失威照<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n性侵罪成 華盛頓前總主教革除聖職"},{"pid":"85281d64605223808bcc09ea038a2662b9e67870","tid":1025091,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T06:04:35.000Z","msg":"習大大夠識用電腦啦 (橙色enter)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DBCi_5QXUAEbLEa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDBCi_5QXUAEbLEa.jpg&h=8e6b3d65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/87e90f81gw1ezeipxjd64j20zk0qo0ut-1024x768.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinadigitaltimes.net%2Fchinese%2Ffiles%2F2015%2F12%2F87e90f81gw1ezeipxjd64j20zk0qo0ut-1024x768.jpg&h=bcbc8664&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79b41e52bd11ddbcb4ce2cfc4de955916afc7779","tid":1025091,"uid":165782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85281d64605223808bcc09ea038a2662b9e67870","tid":1025091,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T06:04:35.000Z","msg":"習大大夠識用電腦啦 (橙色enter)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DBCi_5QXUAEbLEa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDBCi_5QXUAEbLEa.jpg&h=8e6b3d65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/87e90f81gw1ezeipxjd64j20zk0qo0ut-1024x768.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinadigitaltimes.net%2Fchinese%2Ffiles%2F2015%2F12%2F87e90f81gw1ezeipxjd64j20zk0qo0ut-1024x768.jpg&h=bcbc8664&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T06:18:58.000Z","msg":"廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c5f326ce7422de3e7494e219d6e32035d6efbe","tid":1025091,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T08:12:50.000Z","msg":"人地有做gym，好過肥winnie"},{"pid":"80bd08ecea0311ffb0cde360256b28418571b182","tid":1025091,"uid":43428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79b41e52bd11ddbcb4ce2cfc4de955916afc7779","tid":1025091,"uid":165782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor